---
title: Oven-Roasted Greek Kebabs with Lemon Rice and Garlicky Yogurt Dressed Salad
description: These Greek kebabs are mixed with a little yogurt to help make them tender and give an extra flavour boost. Paired with some lemon rice and a cooling salad with garlicky yogurt dressing and you have yourself a Mediterranean feast!
